These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
There 2 different types of food: pomegranate, cranberry
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: tennis, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not the person eating cranberry##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | cranberry   | pomegranate  |
| Sport   | tennis | weightlifting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
There 2 different types of food: plum, zucchini
2 different pets are kept: mouse, horse
1. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
2. the owner of the mouse is not the person eating zucchini##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | plum | zucchini      |
| Pet    | mouse  | horse |

 #################################

 
