.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-7::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  engineer, teacher
2 different pets are kept: hedgehog, snake
1. the engineer is in an odd position##4
2. the engineer is not the owner of the snake##6

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1      |       2       |
| Job   | engineer | teacher |
| Pet   | hedgehog       | snake       |

